<DEFINITION NAME="freesubmit">

<DIV NAME="ALPHA" TITLE="Search Engine Submit">

<BUTTON TYPE="NEXT" TARGET="OMEGA"></BUTTON>
<META TYPE="TITLE">Search Engine Submit - Step 1/1</META>
<META TYPE="DESCRIPTION">
This tool will automatically register your website to many of the free submit search engines, 
this is a great starting point to getting your website out on the Internet. The registration 
will occur within 24 hours so if you have not already done so you should add Meta tags to your website.

In addition to using this tool customers are encouraged to consider looking into using services 
such as Overture or Google AdWord, Yahoo Priority Submission, and Looksmart in addition to using this tool. 

By popular request this tool no longer saves information back to your store settings.
</META>

<INPUT TYPE="TEXTBOX" NAME="channel:zoovy:website_url"  PROMPT="Your Website URL" COLS="45" LOADFROM=""></INPUT>
<INPUT TYPE="TEXTAREA" rows="6" cols="60"  NAME="merchant:zoovy:business_description" PROMPT="Business Description"></INPUT>
<INPUT TYPE="TEXTBOX" NAME="channel:zoovy:email" LOADFROM="merchant:zoovy:support_email,merchant:zoovy:email" PROMPT="Contact Email"></INPUT>
<INPUT TYPE="TEXTBOX" NAME="channel:zoovy:company_name" PROMPT="Company Name" LOADFROM="merchant:zoovy:company_name" COLS="60"></INPUT>
<INPUT TYPE="TEXTBOX" NAME="channel:zoovy:firstname" PROMPT="First Name" LOADFROM="merchant:zoovy:firstname" COLS="20"></INPUT>
<INPUT TYPE="TEXTBOX" NAME="channel:zoovy:lastname" PROMPT="Last Name" LOADFROM="merchant:zoovy:lastname" COLS="20"></INPUT>
<INPUT TYPE="TEXTBOX" NAME="channel:zoovy:address1" PROMPT="Street Address1" LOADFROM="merchant:zoovy:address1" COLS="60"></INPUT>
<INPUT TYPE="TEXTBOX" NAME="channel:zoovy:address2" PROMPT="Street Address2" LOADFROM="merchant:zoovy:address2" COLS="60"></INPUT>
<INPUT TYPE="TEXTBOX" NAME="channel:zoovy:city" PROMPT="City" LOADFROM="merchant:zoovy:city" COLS="25"></INPUT>
<INPUT TYPE="TEXTBOX" NAME="channel:zoovy:state" PROMPT="State" LOADFROM="merchant:zoovy:state" COLS="2"></INPUT>
<INPUT TYPE="TEXTBOX" NAME="channel:zoovy:zip" PROMPT="Zip"  LOADFROM="merchant:zoovy:zip" COLS="5"></INPUT>
<INPUT TYPE="TEXTBOX" NAME="channel:zoovy:country" PROMPT="Country"  LOADFROM="merchant:zoovy:country" COLS="10"></INPUT>
<INPUT TYPE="TEXTBOX" NAME="channel:zoovy:phone" PROMPT="Phone"  LOADFROM="merchant:zoovy:phone" COLS="15"></INPUT>
<INPUT TYPE="TEXTBOX" NAME="channel:zoovy:facsimile" PROMPT="Facsimile"  LOADFROM="merchant:zoovy:facsimile" COLS="15"></INPUT>
<INPUT TYPE="TEXTAREA" rows="3" cols="60" NAME="merchant:zoovy:keywords"  LOADFROM="" PROMPT="Please enter keywords separated by commas"></INPUT>		

<BUTTON TYPE="PEER" TARGET="OMEGA" PROMPT="Review Settings"></BUTTON>

</DIV>

<DIV NAME="OMEGA" TITLE="Review">
<BUTTON TYPE="LAST" PROMPT="Back to Edit Data"></BUTTON>
<META TYPE="TITLE">Search Engine Submit - Review</META>
<META TYPE="DESCRIPTION">Please review your settings.</META>

<DISPLAY TYPE="LABEL">
In the next 24 hours your business will be submitted to over 200 search engines. You will receive email 
confirmations from several of them. Over the next few weeks those search engines will visit the website 
listed below and catalog the pages. While your account is active Zoovy will automatically re-submit your 
site once each month.
</DISPLAY>
	<INPUT TYPE="BLANK"></INPUT>
	<DISPLAY TYPE="BYVALUE" NAME="channel:zoovy:company_name" PROMPT="Company Name" ERROR="Unknown??"></DISPLAY>
	<DISPLAY TYPE="BYVALUE" NAME="channel:zoovy:website_url" PROMPT="Website URL" ERROR="website address not configured"></DISPLAY>
	<DISPLAY TYPE="BYVALUE" NAME="channel:zoovy:keywords" PROMPT="Keywords" ERROR="Unknown??"></DISPLAY>

<BUTTON TYPE="SUBMIT" PROMPT="Register Now!"></BUTTON>

</DIV>

</DEFINITION>